The healthcheck.sh script can be used by nagios to perform a healthcheck.  The usage is:

./healthcheck.sh http://localhost:8080/geonetwork/criticalhealthcheck monitor monitor

or

./healthcheck.sh http://localhost:8080/geonetwork/warninghealthcheck monitor monitor

or

./healthcheck.sh http://localhost:8080/geonetwork/expensivehealthcheck monitor monitor

Where monitor has to have the Monitor profile (or Admin)